{
  "id": "69ede978c1f97bb5673e4907",
  "title": "Good naming is a process, not a single step",
  "created": 1777199484,
  "updated": 1777206248,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ede978c1f97bb5673e4907",
      "text": "Good naming is a process, not a single step",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777199484,
      "updated": 1777199484
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee02a80000000000149beb",
      "text": " [Arlo]さんが書いた記事で、プログラミングの[命名のプロセス]について書いた記事",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777205928,
      "updated": 1777205943
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee02a80000000000149bec",
      "text": "  [Arlo Being Bloody Stupid]というブログの記事の1つ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777205928,
      "updated": 1777205928
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee03c300000000002ff2f9",
      "text": " 1回で完璧な命名をつけるかわりに、修正しながら良いネーミングにしていきましょうというやつ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777206212,
      "updated": 1777206227
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee025f0000000000149bcd",
      "text": " > Many people try to come up with a great name all at once. This is hard and rarely works well. The problem is that naming is design: it is picking the correct place for each thing and creating the right abstraction. Doing that perfectly the first time is unlikely. Let’s talk about evolutionary naming. (...)",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777205855,
      "updated": 1777205874
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee029d0000000000149bdd",
      "text": "  https://arlobelshee.com/good-naming-is-a-process-not-a-single-step/ ([Web Archive https://web.archive.org/web/20180319011316/https://arlobelshee.com/good-naming-is-a-process-not-a-single-step/])",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777205917,
      "updated": 1777205917
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee029d0000000000149bde",
      "text": "   https://www.digdeeproots.com/articles/on/naming-as-a-process/ ([Web Archive https://web.archive.org/web/20200421135422/https://www.digdeeproots.com/articles/on/naming-as-a-process/])",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777205917,
      "updated": 1777205924
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee025f0000000000149bcf",
      "text": "  > 多くの人が、1回で最高の命名をしようとする。これは難しく、うまく行くことなんて滅多にない。問題はネーミングというのは設計であるということだ。あらゆるものに収まりの良い場所を与え、正しい抽象化をしなくてはならない。これを最初の1回で完璧にこなせる可能性は低い。だから[進化的ネーミング]について話をしよう。",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777205855,
      "updated": 1777205901
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee02830000000000149bd2",
      "text": "   和訳→ [/kawasima/命名のプロセス]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777205892,
      "updated": 1777205914
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee03d400000000002ff2fa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777206228,
      "updated": 1777206228
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee03dd00000000002ff2fd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777206237,
      "updated": 1777206237
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee03d400000000002ff2fb",
      "text": "まだちょっとしか読んでないのに要約を書いた[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777206228,
      "updated": 1777206248
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee03df00000000002ff2fe",
